data.description: Country living at its finest! This beautiful 5 bedroom home, located on 5 acres, is less than 10 minutes away from scenic downtown Woodruff. With easy access to Greenville and Spartanburg.  Enjoy a cup of coffee on your secluded back deck, with the peaceful views of nature. This expansive lot, with no HOA, boasts mature trees and access to a creek.    Some of the home features include: Large master bedroom with walk-in closet with built in shelving. Spacious master bath with a beautiful tub and separate shower. Generous sized closets in the bedrooms. Solar panels. Rustic fireplace with gas logs, and granite counters in the kitchen.  Some of the property features include: a well and additional septic on the back portion of the property. Flat, buildable land for future expansion, with the ability to sub-divide if desired.  Schedule your appointment today!
